{"tid":2206672,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"無立案法團唐樓 收到「強制驗樓計劃通知不獲遵從」 求救！","createTime":"2020-09-17T15:24:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T02:05:07.000Z","uid":201508,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1f03abddef3291bd5de46aac00709677a9879fa6","tid":2206672,"uid":201508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T15:24:50.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲，<br />\n<br />\n在下同老母住緊無立案法團唐樓，早前收到「強制驗樓計劃通知」，但由於無立案法團，根本無辦法完成強制驗樓計劃。<br />\n<br />\n請問各位巴絲有無遇過呢種情況？會唔會被告上法庭罰成幾萬蚊？<br />\n<br />\n有無可能可以向屋宇署申請延期？<br />\n<br />\n真係救命求助！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e61c5de897fcbeb4e428ebbca4a42f57872f46e","tid":2206672,"uid":64603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T15:25:55.000Z","msg":"搵區議員啦"},{"pid":"feaca5dd7a4add87f4851ac29935ace83359e005","tid":2206672,"uid":87122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1f03abddef3291bd5de46aac00709677a9879fa6","tid":2206672,"uid":201508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T15:24:50.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲，<br />\n<br />\n在下同老母住緊無立案法團唐樓，早前收到「強制驗樓計劃通知」，但由於無立案法團，根本無辦法完成強制驗樓計劃。<br />\n<br />\n請問各位巴絲有無遇過呢種情況？會唔會被告上法庭罰成幾萬蚊？<br />\n<br />\n有無可能可以向屋宇署申請延期？<br />\n<br />\n真係救命求助！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T15:28:46.000Z","msg":"會出幾次通知，跟住釘契，最好搵民政署問下先，叫佢地搞居民會叫大家成立法團。<br />\n<br />\n大維修最好親力親為，淨係做驗樓必須執修項目，好多公司搵食，最後變天價工程"},{"pid":"02ad47e180a92888228b86ca4e646ef4d20fb77e","tid":2206672,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T15:32:51.000Z","msg":"住公屋就唔會有呢d問題"},{"pid":"93397463e9bdeba5c37588403b30f07fbe4eb66e","tid":2206672,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T15:33:04.000Z","msg":"呢啲野都係拖字訣"},{"pid":"7015edc1a9d97484fb6eabc4f994e4d145e06627","tid":2206672,"uid":201508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T15:34:04.000Z","msg":"請問，封粉紅色信，可唔可以唔理，等佢釘契就算？<br />\n已經收到粉紅色信，話如果唔做，「一經定罪，可被處50000元」。<br />\n係唔係即係話，下一步就會告我？<br />\n小弟窮撚一名，真係無錢俾罰款o架。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前試過搵區議員，區議員話會安排社工，不過可能因為疫情，所以無左下文。"},{"pid":"56b15ac6a818642ab5ec5f8cf85c0eafa04b21f5","tid":2206672,"uid":57961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T15:34:10.000Z","msg":"可以直接send email去屋宇署申請延期，通常係3個月"},{"pid":"5daba9162a40b6e607c728caff66ae6b6bb02898","tid":2206672,"uid":264301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T15:37:36.000Z","msg":"盡量搵黃區議員先<br />\n好多民賤聯議員都同d工程公司有利益瓜葛"},{"pid":"d146467007db323996ac0fe3411287d823098775","tid":2206672,"uid":19743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56b15ac6a818642ab5ec5f8cf85c0eafa04b21f5","tid":2206672,"uid":57961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T15:34:10.000Z","msg":"可以直接send email去屋宇署申請延期，通常係3個月"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T15:40:46.000Z","msg":"無報價單基本上唔會批EOT"},{"pid":"919a473c170f7646df728f8c220f